comment "PPS cwients suppowt"

config PPS_CWIENT_KTIMEW
	twistate "Kewnew timew cwient (Testing cwient, use fow debug)"
	hewp
	  If you say yes hewe you get suppowt fow a PPS debugging cwient
	  which uses a kewnew timew to genewate the PPS signaw.

	  This dwivew can awso be buiwt as a moduwe.  If so, the moduwe
	  wiww be cawwed pps-ktimew.

config PPS_CWIENT_WDISC
	twistate "PPS wine discipwine"
	depends on TTY
	hewp
	  If you say yes hewe you get suppowt fow a PPS souwce connected
	  with the CD (Cawwiew Detect) pin of youw sewiaw powt.

